@page "/"
@attribute [AllowAnonymous]

<PageMeta Title="ScamAlert — remote-access alerts for your Windows PCs"
          Description="Detect suspicious remote desktop and similar access on your PCs. $7.99/month single-user license with SMS alerts."
          CanonicalPath="/" />

<section class="hero-sa mb-5">
    <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
            <p class="text-uppercase small fw-semibold text-sa-accent mb-2">Remote-access detection</p>
            <h1 class="display-6 fw-semibold mb-3">Know when someone tries to reach your PC—before the session turns into a scam.</h1>
            <p class="lead text-secondary">
                ScamAlert watches inbound RDP, SSH, and Telnet on the Windows machines you register.
                When access looks suspicious, <strong>you get the SMS</strong>—fast, direct, no call center in the middle.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-3"><span class="badge rounded-pill badge-sa">$7.99/month · single-user license</span></p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/signup">Get started</a>
                <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" href="/pricing">See pricing</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5">
            <div class="card border-0 hero-card">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h2 class="h5 mb-3">Built like infrastructure software</h2>
                    <ul class="mb-0 text-secondary sa-checklist">
                        <li>Lightweight Windows agent—no kernel driver in v1</li>
                        <li>Alert the contacts you configure via SMS</li>
                        <li>Catch unexpected remote sessions during tech-support scams</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-5">
    <h2 class="h4 mb-4 text-center">What you get</h2>
    <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="h6 text-sa-accent">Early warning</h3>
                    <p class="small text-secondary mb-0">See remote-access attempts on ports criminals abuse during refund and support scams.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="h6 text-sa-accent">Your contacts</h3>
                    <p class="small text-secondary mb-0">Route SMS to your phone and a backup contact—no shared family plan required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="h6 text-sa-accent">Simple license</h3>
                    <p class="small text-secondary mb-0">One account, $7.99/month. Add PCs under your subscription from the dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-5 py-4 px-3 rounded sa-muted-panel">
    <h2 class="h4 mb-4">How it works</h2>
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <h3 class="h6">Subscribe &amp; sign in</h3>
            <p class="small text-secondary">Create your account and complete checkout.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <h3 class="h6">Install on your PC</h3>
            <p class="small text-secondary">Pair each Windows machine from the portal with a one-time code.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <h3 class="h6">Get alerted</h3>
            <p class="small text-secondary">Suspicious remote access triggers SMS so you can verify and respond.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center mb-0 mt-3">
        <a href="/how-it-works">Full walkthrough</a> · <a href="/pricing">$7.99/month license</a>
    </p>
</section>

<section class="text-center mb-4">
    <h2 class="h4 mb-2">Security that feels like a modern dev tool</h2>
    <p class="text-secondary col-lg-8 mx-auto">
        ScamAlert does not replace good security hygiene—it adds a focused signal when remote access shows up uninvited.
    </p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Start your license</a>
</section>
